OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 17 JUL
OL,4,CRADIO TRANSMITTERS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1987FThe second of two 7am - 7pm
OL,7,Fperiods of planned work on the
OL,8,FDroitwich transmitters to replace
OL,9,Fageing parts on the aerial system. The
OL,10,Ffollowing advice is offered to
OL,11,Flisteners:
OL,12,
OL,13,FIn the Midlands:
OL,14,F- For BBC Radio 1: retune to 1089Khz.
OL,15,F- For BBC Radio 2: retune to 909Khz or
OL,16,Fuse VHF/FM.
OL,17,F- For BBC Radio 3: use VHF/FM.
OL,18,
OL,19,FAcross England:
OL,20,F- For BBC Radio 4: use VHF/FM whilst
OL,21,F200Khz LW is unavailable.
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
